ygData.subject: Re: [EverQuest] Digest Number 592
ygData.msgSnippet: Cool.  I decided to forego the leggings and tunic for the quest armor.  I was given a dwarven ringmail tunic which works just as well.  I figured I d go back
ygData.messageBody:
Cool. I decided to forego the leggings and tunic for the quest armor. I
was given a dwarven ringmail tunic which works just as well. I figured I'd
go back to EC and try to gain a few levels, then if I haven't gotten
something better by level 15 I'd go back and deal with the Slavers. I still
have all the components in the bank so all I would need are the fibulas.

I'll look for Genmay though.

Airbourne
Wulfric
Raido
(the name depends which server I'm on)





> Sweet! Hey if my warrior is online, (Genmay), gimmie a hollar and I'll
help with the Orc slavers. We'll also try and grab a cleric too! never hurts
to have an extra healer around! I might be on tonight, (9-25) but I'm not
sure.
>

> > Okay the Orc Fingerbones drop off of Orc Pawns in G-Fay. That's where I
got both of mine. There is a bandit camp in G-Fay and I killed exactly two
bandits and got the golden bandit tooth. So now it's down to the Orc
Fibulas. I need 2 of them. One of the legplates, one for the tunic. From
what I hear these drop off Orc Slavers in the cave in Crushbone. My ranger
is level 10 and I've had no trouble acquiring any of these items. The Orc
Slavers con yellow to me at 10. I can kill them with help.
